<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 22:06:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于胡塞武装袭击，数千只羔羊和小牛被困在运往以色列的船上，处境悲惨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-livestock-stuck-on-ship-to-israel-in-dire-conditions-due-to-houthi-attacks/0000018d-60ab-d897-a3ef-e3bba9140000</link><description>由于目前红海的安全威胁，该船已两次改道，将启程为期一个月的航行。非政府组织以色列反对生鲜运输呼吁农业部“停止这种疯狂行为”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-livestock-stuck-on-ship-to-israel-in-dire-conditions-due-to-houthi-attacks/0000018d-60ab-d897-a3ef-e3bba9140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队占领加沙房屋，然后将其烧毁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-occupies-gaza-homes-then-burns-them-down/0000018d-6021-d16e-a39f-7f3f01e30000</link><description>《国土报》获得的信息显示，以色列国防军指挥官在未经法律批准的情况下命令士兵放火烧毁加沙废弃房屋。数百处已遭到不可挽回的损坏</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 20:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-occupies-gaza-homes-then-burns-them-down/0000018d-6021-d16e-a39f-7f3f01e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列精锐部队军官在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/officer-in-elite-israeli-army-unit-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-60fa-d99b-abaf-e7fe11510000</link><description>来自以色列北部的 36 岁少校伊扎尔·霍夫曼 (Yizhar Hofman) 在周三的战斗中身亡。 10月7日，参加贝埃里基布兹战役</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 19:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/officer-in-elite-israeli-army-unit-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-60fa-d99b-abaf-e7fe11510000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔对美国犹太人和白宫的求爱达到高潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-31/ty-article/.highlight/qatars-courtship-of-u-s-jews-and-the-white-house-comes-to-a-climax/0000018d-607c-d897-a3ef-e3fd3f820000</link><description>美国犹太领导人和两党议员对卡塔尔未能充分利用其对哈马斯的影响力越来越不耐烦，他们的挫败感正以前所未有的方式显现出来</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:50:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-31/ty-article/.highlight/qatars-courtship-of-u-s-jews-and-the-white-house-comes-to-a-climax/0000018d-607c-d897-a3ef-e3fd3f820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 LGBTQ 团体批评针对极端正统成员的“犹太手机法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lgbtq-groups-criticize-kosher-cell-phone-law-for-ultra-orthodox-members/0000018d-6023-d5e3-abfd-75fb04380000</link><description>议会委员会将听取一项新的“犹太手机法”提案，该法将阻止 LGBTQ 求助热线通过拉比认证的手机提供 24/7 服务，因此不被视为紧急服务</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 17:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lgbtq-groups-criticize-kosher-cell-phone-law-for-ultra-orthodox-members/0000018d-6023-d5e3-abfd-75fb04380000</guid></item><item><title>“令人沮丧的是保持沉默”：以色列-巴勒斯坦和平组织回应 BDS 的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/disheartening-to-be-silenced-israeli-palestinian-peace-group-responds-to-bds-claims/0000018d-5fe0-d7f9-a3af-dfe86c950000</link><description>“站在一起”运动被 BDS 贴上“思想上不诚实”的标签，导致该组织发表声明强调“争取巴勒斯坦解放的斗争是多方面的”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 15:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/disheartening-to-be-silenced-israeli-palestinian-peace-group-responds-to-bds-claims/0000018d-5fe0-d7f9-a3af-dfe86c950000</guid></item><item><title>为什么 BDS 不能容忍以色列的犹太人和巴勒斯坦人站在一起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-bds-cant-tolerate-jews-and-palestinians-in-israel-standing-together/0000018d-5f07-d4f8-a9df-5f2f88ca0000</link><description>“站在一起”是以色列一项快速发展的草根运动，旨在将犹太人和阿拉伯人团结在一起。它对抗占领，它处于反对加沙战争抗议的最前线，它探视人质的家人。现在，一个重要的 BDS 组织正在呼吁抵制它</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 15:09:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-bds-cant-tolerate-jews-and-palestinians-in-israel-standing-together/0000018d-5f07-d4f8-a9df-5f2f88ca0000</guid></item><item><title>随着提名结束，加沙和乌克兰成为诺贝尔和平奖议程的首要议题；以色列组织提名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/gaza-and-ukraine-on-top-of-nobel-peace-prize-agenda-israeli-orgs-nominated/0000018d-5f18-d4f8-a9df-5f3c7fba0000</link><description>由 10 月 7 日受害者维维安·西尔弗 (Vivian Silver) 共同创立的以色列组织 Women Wage Peace 是该奖项的提名之一。在大约 300 名提名中，许多人与加沙和乌克兰的战争有关，其中包括驻加沙记者莫塔兹·阿扎伊萨 (Motaz Azaiza)</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/gaza-and-ukraine-on-top-of-nobel-peace-prize-agenda-israeli-orgs-nominated/0000018d-5f18-d4f8-a9df-5f3c7fba0000</guid></item><item><title>“这个政府把我们带到了不好的地方”：以色列的抗议运动重新回到街头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-31/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-taking-us-bad-places-israels-protest-movements-are-back/0000018d-5b09-d6b0-adcd-7fbb8d6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-31/ty-article-podcast/the-government-is-taking-us-bad-places-israels-protest-movements-are-back/0000018d-5b09-d6b0-adcd-7fbb8d6b0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这位以色列艺术家不会参加她在南非举办的展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-artist-has-a-new-exhibition-in-south-africa-she-wont-be-attending/0000018d-5b13-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fe5b30000</link><description>以色列艺术家莫兰·克利格 (Moran Kliger) 原定飞往开普敦参加她的展览开幕式，但 10 月 7 日的袭击、加沙持续的战争以及海牙审判造成的以色列和南非之间的敌意让她感到出发不安全</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-artist-has-a-new-exhibition-in-south-africa-she-wont-be-attending/0000018d-5b13-d0fc-a9bd-5f5fe5b30000</guid></item><item><title>纸上的恐怖：以色列人于 10 月 7 日设计出迷人的海报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/horror-on-paper-israeli-designers-made-captivating-posters-on-october-7/0000018d-5f13-d0af-a3af-7fbf4e210000</link><description>一个关于哈马斯袭击的展览将有 70 张海报印在 70 x 70 厘米的纸上，分为七个类别</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/horror-on-paper-israeli-designers-made-captivating-posters-on-october-7/0000018d-5f13-d0af-a3af-7fbf4e210000</guid></item><item><title>“我的教室用品是一块橡皮和一把 AK-47”：以色列顶级讽刺节目嘲笑近东救济工程处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/my-classroom-supplies-are-an-eraser-and-an-ak-47-top-israeli-satire-show-mocks-unrwa/0000018d-5f39-d4f8-a9df-5f3dd12b0000</link><description>以色列最受欢迎的喜剧小品节目《Eretz Nehederet》在最近 10 月 7 日发生与哈马斯有关联的指控后嘲笑了近东救济工程处。其中还有一位虚构的联合国秘书长，他对近东救济工程处感到震惊，他说，“当然，我认为我们需要将他们的资金增加一倍”</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/my-classroom-supplies-are-an-eraser-and-an-ak-47-top-israeli-satire-show-mocks-unrwa/0000018d-5f39-d4f8-a9df-5f3dd12b0000</guid></item><item><title>她儿时的大屠杀梦想使这位以色列电影制片人一路登上了奥斯卡奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-animator-hoping-to-become-the-first-israeli-woman-to-win-an-oscar/0000018d-5b7d-de55-a99d-ff7fcfc10000</link><description>塔尔·坎特 (Tal Kantor) 希望在 10 月份访问好莱坞宣传她的动画短片《给猪的信》，但加沙战争改变了一切，包括人们对她获得奥斯卡提名的感人作品的反应，该作品讲述了大屠杀幸存者以及同情心和同情心的力量。共情</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-01-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-animator-hoping-to-become-the-first-israeli-woman-to-win-an-oscar/0000018d-5b7d-de55-a99d-ff7fcfc10000</guid></item><item><title>挪威敦促维持近东救济工程处的资金，表示没有收到以色列关于指控的通报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/norway-urges-maintaining-unrwa-funding-says-it-wasnt-briefed-by-israel-on-allegations/0000018d-5eef-d4f8-a9df-5fef0bbe0000</link><description>这个斯堪的纳维亚国家敦促近东救济工程处的其他捐助国“反思更广泛的后果”，因为有报道称其员工参与了哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织 10 月 7 日的袭击，因此削减了资金。挪威外交部长表示，近东救济工程处是加沙 150 万难民的重要生命线</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/norway-urges-maintaining-unrwa-funding-says-it-wasnt-briefed-by-israel-on-allegations/0000018d-5eef-d4f8-a9df-5fef0bbe0000</guid></item><item><title>唱片公司因反以色列言论而终止与罗杰·沃特斯的合同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/record-company-cuts-contract-with-roger-waters-amid-history-of-anti-israel-statements/0000018d-5ecf-d0fc-a9bd-5edf3f6a0000</link><description>《综艺》杂志网站报道称，这家德国公司此举也是继平克·弗洛伊德乐队创始人过去发表反对以色列、美国以及支持俄罗斯总统普京的言论之后做出的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:01:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/record-company-cuts-contract-with-roger-waters-amid-history-of-anti-israel-statements/0000018d-5ecf-d0fc-a9bd-5edf3f6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了周二在加沙地带战斗中丧生的三名预备役军人的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-reservists-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018d-5e49-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d93a00000</link><description>军方还表示，周二有五名士兵在加沙的战斗中受重伤。他们正在接受治疗，并已通知家人</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:53:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/israeli-army-names-three-reservists-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-tuesday/0000018d-5e49-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d93a00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的前幕僚长将阿里·哈罗 (Ari Harow) 被判犯有欺诈和违反信任罪的国家证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ex-chief-of-staff-ari-harow-convicted-of-fraud-breach-of-trust/0000018d-5e72-d0af-a3af-7efea9360000</link><description>哈罗被指控从一家他保留所有权的公司获取利润，尽管他在上任前被勒令出售自己的部分</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-ex-chief-of-staff-ari-harow-convicted-of-fraud-breach-of-trust/0000018d-5e72-d0af-a3af-7efea9360000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，据信被哈马斯关押在加沙的以色列警察被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-thought-to-be-hamas-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-on-october-7/0000018d-5e20-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d20b30000</link><description>吉利是10月7日遇害的61名警察之一。吉利是以色列南部梅塔尔的居民，10月7日正在休病假，当他了解到发生紧急情况时，他决定前往内盖夫西部</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 07:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-officer-thought-to-be-hamas-hostage-in-gaza-was-killed-on-october-7/0000018d-5e20-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d20b30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡目前的联盟将无法在与哈马斯的人质协议中幸存</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-is-doomed-whether-israel-agrees-to-a-hostage-deal-or-not/0000018d-5bde-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf39740000</link><description>以色列总理正接近一个关键的决策点：是在做出重大让步的情况下接受该协议并面临许多以色列人的批评，还是按照极右翼部长本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇的要求拒绝该协议，从而冒着中间派部长离开的风险。与此同时，他采取了含糊的半否认态度</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-is-doomed-whether-israel-agrees-to-a-hostage-deal-or-not/0000018d-5bde-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf39740000</guid></item><item><title>没有人相信卡汉主义者空洞地威胁要推翻内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/nobody-believes-the-kahanists-empty-threats-to-topple-the-israeli-government/0000018d-5c1e-d4f8-a9df-5f3ef2680000</link><description>鉴于他们没有参与战争的管理，驱逐加沙巴勒斯坦人的支持者们一直与甘茨的中间派政党发生冲突 — — 主要是因为该党在民意调查中的支持率飙升。即使本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇反对人质交易，他们也不会走完整九码</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-31/ty-article/.premium/nobody-believes-the-kahanists-empty-threats-to-topple-the-israeli-government/0000018d-5c1e-d4f8-a9df-5f3ef2680000</guid></item></channel></rss>